    "content": "# Firmcraft Documentation Index\n\nAll internal documentation for the Firmcraft platform. The [ROADMAP.md](../ROADMAP.md) is the central hub — start there for the big picture.\n\n---\n\n## Product & Strategy\n\n| Document | Description |\n|----------|-------------|\n| [ROADMAP.md](../ROADMAP.md) | Central product roadmap — Phases 1-6, pricing, competitive positioning, milestones |\n| [billing-spec.md](billing-spec.md) | Billing model — Spark/Flow/Forge tiers, Stripe product/price IDs, metered overages |\n| [brand-strategy-actions.md](brand-strategy-actions.md) | Action items from brand strategy review — trademark filings, brand architecture, marketing |\n| [site-copy-vs-hermes-audit.md](site-copy-vs-hermes-audit.md) | Audit of site copy claims vs. actual Hermes capabilities — oversells, undersells, gaps |\n| [firmcraft-weekend-buildout-plan.md](firmcraft-weekend-buildout-plan.md) | Master buildout plan — Hermes assessment, 9 workstreams, multi-app architecture |\n| [alternative-funding-research.md](../alternative-funding-research.md) | Funding options research — RBF, indie VC, SBA loans, SBIR grants, cloud credits |\n\n## Phase 1: AI Phone Answering\n\n| Document | Description |\n|----------|-------------|\n| [PHASE1-AI-PHONE-ANSWERING-SPEC.md](PHASE1-AI-PHONE-ANSWERING-SPEC.md) | Full technical spec — Vapi comparison, Hermes skill design, voice agent prompt, cost analysis |\n| [PHASE1-DECISIONS.md](PHASE1-DECISIONS.md) | Decision log — Pipecat over Vapi, Deepgram Nova-3 + Cartesia Sonic-3, deployment modes |\n\n## Phase 2: Scheduling + Dispatch\n\n| Document | Description |\n|----------|-------------|\n| [scheduling-dispatch-architecture.md](scheduling-dispatch-architecture.md) | System architecture — data model, dispatch engine, mobile app, real-time infra, API design |\n| [scheduling-dispatch-build-plan.md](scheduling-dispatch-build-plan.md) | Execution plan — 5 build phases, 14-week timeline, risk register, testing strategy, GTM |\n| [scheduling-dispatch-market-research.md](scheduling-dispatch-market-research.md) | Competitive intelligence — ServiceTitan, Jobber, HCP teardowns, contractor needs, AI strategy |\n| [ai-scheduling-dispatch-research.md](ai-scheduling-dispatch-research.md) | AI/ML research — VRP solvers (VROOM, OR-Tools, PyVRP), predictive scheduling, smart dispatching |\n\n## Phase 6: Digital Ops\n\n| Document | Description |\n|----------|-------------|\n| [digital-ops-research.md](digital-ops-research.md) | Module research — existing assets, open-source tools (Postiz, Lighthouse, Listmonk, n8n), architecture |\n| [gbp-setup-plan.md](gbp-setup-plan.md) | End-to-end GBP setup plan — 3-phase approach, timeline, critical path for Digital Ops |\n| [gbp-api-application-checklist.md](gbp-api-application-checklist.md) | Execute-ready checklist for GBP API access application — 9-step process, drafted use case |\n\n## Sales & Prospecting\n\n| Document | Description |\n|----------|-------------|\n| [houston-hvac-prospect-research.md](houston-hvac-prospect-research.md) | Houston HVAC prospect database — 115 active prospects scored 1-5, detailed profiles |\n| [us-transactions-company.md](../us-transactions-company.md) | UST onboarding survey (company profile) — pre-filled research about US Transactions Corp |\n| [us-transactions-individual.md](../us-transactions-individual.md) | UST onboarding survey (individual profile) — template for contact assessment |\n\n## Infrastructure & Setup\n\n| Document | Description |\n|----------|-------------|\n| [cloudflare-access-setup.md](../cloudflare-access-setup.md) | Cloudflare Zero Trust Access — setup for firmcraft.ai subdomains, Google/Microsoft SSO |\n| [firmcraft-google-workspace-setup.md](firmcraft-google-workspace-setup.md) | Google Workspace email — DKIM, DMARC, SPF, domain verification, OAuth re-auth runbook |\n| [resend-firmcraft-mail-setup.md](resend-firmcraft-mail-setup.md) | Outreach sending subdomain (mail.firmcraft.ai) — blocked on Resend plan upgrade |\n| [firmcraft-credentials-template.md](firmcraft-credentials-template.md) | Blank credentials template for new deployments |\n",
